nNewEra"}, "content": "Poppintree Park in Ballymun, Ireland. \n\nA father confronts a group of invaders alleged to be targeting his child.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 9838}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBhDLQJl", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 1117, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "hat", "id": 8701359, "raw_content": "You'd be surprised at how many bleeding-heart leftists actually don't comprehend that the illegals here *are not stateless, free-roaming refugees with nowhere to go if we don't take them in.*\n\nIt doesn't register with them that every last one of these people is actually a *full citizen of some other country.*\n\nWe should stop saying, \"Illegals shouldn't vote in U.S. elections.\" \n\nWe should start saying, \"CITIZENS OF FOREIGN NATIONS shouldn't vote in U.S. elections.\"\n\nThen watch the look on their faces as they struggle to understand what you mean. \"What citizens? What are you talking about?\"\n\nIt's astounding how many of them do NOT comprehend this.\n\nMaybe a small change in terminology would help. \n\nRight now, I'd take anything that would help even a little.\n", "author": "Cuetardian", "created": 1782574460862, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Valiazaner", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "A Modest Proposal: Stop saying \"Illegals Shouldn't Vote in U.S. Elections.\" Instead, say, \"Citizens of Foreign Nations Shouldn't Vote in U.S. Elections.\"", "last_comment_created": 1782634723311, "content": "<p>You'd be surprised at how many bleeding-heart leftists actually don't comprehend that the illegals here <em>are not stateless, free-roaming refugees with nowhere to go if we don't take them in.</em></p>\n<p>It doesn't register with them that every last one of these people is actually a <em>full citizen of some other country.</em></p>\n<p>We should stop saying, &quot;Illegals shouldn't vote in U.S. elections.&quot;</p>\n<p>We should start saying, &quot;CITIZENS OF FOREIGN NATIONS shouldn't vote in U.S. elections.&quot;</p>\n<p>Then watch the look on their faces as they struggle to understand what you mean. &quot;What citizens? What are you talking about?&quot;</p>\n<p>It's astounding how many of them do NOT comprehend this.</p>\n<p>Maybe a small change in terminology would help.</p>\n<p>Right now, I'd take anything that would help even a little.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 120, "score_up": 1117, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "SAVE AMERICA", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBhEUutt", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 17, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8702739, "raw_content": "", "author": "wst4", "created": 1782656209127, "profile_picture": "K15ahGsDhQtO", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "PeterMcCallister", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.patriots.win", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBhEUutt.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.patriots.win/post/AYO5JPP9cugV.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/PHIL8NvltcaUjmJU.jpeg", "width": 503, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "UBFr06Nw0y%20M-UXm-WOZbF#8EM